Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: End-consumers of industrial products group – organizations and individuals, interested in purchasing products directly from manufacturers, and aiming at reducing level of risks, get high-quality technical support from industrial products manufacturers, and also convenient and smooth-running service of product shipping and guaranteed delivery.  Yodse will become the largest online ecosystem for the most comfortable, rapid and profitable cooperation between industrial products manufacturers and customers in CIS, Asian and African countries, Europe and USA. Introduction of decentralized and transparent ecosystem Yodse based on blockchain technology ensures success to all participants on the B2B trade marketplace. Customers – are individual and legal persons, interested in purchasing essential goods from manufacturers.

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: The main advantage of the global ecosystem Yodse compared to other platforms is the transparency of transactions available on the marketplace owing to the blockchain technology, it will be also possible to make payments in cryptocurrencies. Ecosystem provides users with 24/7/365 system support, available localization of products, direct prices for products from manufacturers. One of the main distinctive features of this marketplace from other world competitors will be a transparent system of feedbacks by real buyers, whose transactions are confirmed by smart contracts. The marketplace will allow users to easily navigate the machine building market, derive maximum benefit from purchase and acquire quality goods without overpaying to intermediaries for their services. Yodse ecosystem is a unique platform owing to a number of advantages over other platforms. For more detals please read WP.

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: The market of industrial group of products Today, the market of industrial group of products has billions of participants, most of whom are increasingly turning to online trading services. And there is nothing surprising in this because the constantly evolving technology allows to make the process of buying and selling as simple and fast as possible. However, to date, there is still no direct relationship between product manufacturers and buyers, which entails the need to involvi ntermediarye in the process, additional financial and time losses.  This situation on the market has served as a basis for the emergence of our Yodse project, which has been developed by our professional team to provide direct communication between manufacturers and end users of industrial products. We strive to erase the boundaries as much as possible and reduce the distance between producers and buyers in the real sector of the economy, increase the efficiency of processes and businesses, making them as transparent as possible through the use of blockchain technology.  Yodse is a global ecosystem that establishes a direct link between producers and buyers of manufactured goods! Get to know our project on its official website https://yodse.io

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: The ecosystem is done to to provide the widest choice of  high quality products for consumers with a direct guarantee from the manufacturer. Its aim is to reduce the costs associated with the search of the products at a low price.   Interesting enough! As you know, the world of finance shows the greatest interest in blockchain technology. However, the functionality of this distributed registry technology is much broader than the financial services industry and can be used not only in the banking sector but also in a number of other areas — to protect copyright and property rights, simplify cash payments, purchase of goods on the blockchain, for data management, mining and energy, digital identification, electronic voting, games, organizational management, on the Internet of things, the labor market, real estate and other areas.  Especially interesting is the use of blockchain technology in the industrial sector, as here it can solve many problems in the organization of production and sale of products. Supply chains of industrial enterprises are very complex mechanisms with their own nuances that can slow down and complicate many production and logistics processes.  The use of blockchain technology will simplify the process of spare parts replacement and purchase of new equipment for industrial companies, will make it possible to track all stages of delivery and get rid of bureaucracy, exclude the intermediary link from the chain and expand the list of customers, as well as establish direct communication with consumers.  Despite the fact that blockchain is still a relatively new technology which continues to develop, it has great prospects and is able to radically change the conduct of business by industrial companies.

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: The market of industrial group of products Today, the market of industrial group of products has billions of participants, most of whom are increasingly turning to online trading services. And there is nothing surprising in this because the constantly evolving technology allows to make the process of buying and selling as simple and fast as possible. However, to date, there is still no direct relationship between product manufacturers and buyers, which entails the need to involvi ntermediarye in the process, additional financial and time losses.  This situation on the market has served as a basis for the emergence of our Yodse project, which has been developed by our professional team to provide direct communication between manufacturers and end users of industrial products. We strive to erase the boundaries as much as possible and reduce the distance between producers and buyers in the real sector of the economy, increase the efficiency of processes and businesses, making them as transparent as possible through the use of blockchain technology.  Yodse is a global ecosystem that establishes a direct link between producers and buyers of manufactured goods! Get to know our project on its official website https://yodse.io

Author: yodse2018
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: There are many markers for checking the quality of products from the manufacturer, including: the availability of certificates, permits, production conditions, control purchases of goods, independent examination, expert analysis of competitive products, as well as one of the most effective and non-paying tools - rating system and reviews of the product. The most important point is that the products placed on the Yodse platform are products from reliable manufacturers interested in the prosperous future of their company. Currently, Yodse has developed a mechanism for selecting and attracting bona fide producers to the platform. We have specialists of this kind and this mechanism is one of the exclusive receptions of the Yodse ecosystem.

Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: Feedback and rating system are the tools for quality control check. It’s worth noting that quality control of products from manufacturers is a complex approach that Yodse platform will perform. Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: Pre-sale of Yodse has started! Yodse is a global ecosystem that directly connects manufacturers and buyers of goods and is based on blockchain technology. In April 2018 the project has come to the Pre-ICO.  In 2017, the concept of yodse blockchain platform was developed. The project was originated by the creators of “VST” , a company specializing in international shipments of manufactured goods. Its employees, assessing the prospects of development, drew attention to the fact that today online sales are gaining popularity. Further analysis showed that in the online environment, the sale of industrial goods is associated with certain difficulties — there is no direct connection between the seller and the buyer, the cost of the goods is often overestimated, and the quality is mediocre.  According to experts, the best way to solve this problem will be to create a global ecosystem based on blockchain technologies. The creation and launch of the platform Yodse will allow you to solve the following tasks:  Communication without intermediaries-sellers and buyers can communicate directly. Reliability of information — decentralized storage of information ensures its inviolability and immutability. Security-it is guaranteed by smart contracts, encryption algorithms and hash functions. Openness-the information is publicly available and any member of the system can track the data of a block. For example, one user transferred $ 100 USD to another, everyone can follow the transaction. Another thing is that information about the parties to the transaction can only be opened by its participants. Creation of yodse ecosystem will allow to organize producers, buyers and service companies into a single community. To manage the system, a Web-interface and a mobile application are developed that will help the buyer to enter the online trading platform, where manufacturers, using a similar service, place offers of their goods and services. At the conclusion of the transaction the parties in real time stipulate its terms after which the buyer pays for the goods. Initially, the money debited from the purse of the buyer shall be credited to Yodse, the manufacturer, upon notice, ships the goods, delivered by transporting service company — a party of the system. Upon completion of the delivery, the logistics company sends a notification and the funds are credited to the seller’s account. The calculation can be carried out both in traditional and in virtual currency. In fact, yodse ecosystem contributes to the development of the industrial sector of the global economy, provoking a decline in the prices of such goods and improving their quality, which has a positive impact on the living standards of the population. Learn more https://yodse.io/ru/

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: Quote regarding the refferal program  Token buyers in the period of pre-ICO and ICO for any amount become participants of referral program and are paid a reward of 5% of the amount of purchases of referrals involved. The first buyers of tokens in the period of pre-ICO and ICO to the amount of at least 1 000 USD are provided with an increased referral rate by 7% compared to the usual token holders. The referral fund of tokens in the amount of 10% of the total issued amount is locked until the 1 January 2019 (except referral payments within the period of pre-ICO and ICO),and further payments to the referrals will be available from the 1 January 2019 in accordance with the referral program.  The purchase of tokens at the early stages will allow purchasers and active holders to influence on the increase of token value, through the referral program. The referral program will be expanded and aimed exclusively at increasing the number of product manufacturers and customers on the marketplace and transactions in the Yodse ecosystem that will contribute to its expansion. These restrictions will not allow to collapse the token value on the stock exchange shortly after the ICO and will set limits to the appearance of a significant number of tokens publicly available on the exchange, as was the case with a large number of ICOs conducted. Thus, we take care that our token buyers funds won’t be affected by the actions of speculators manipulating sales in exchange trade. Moreover, lock of tokens due tothe Yodse team proves its interests and prospects for long-term work and successful implementation of the Yodse project.   Project team is interested in the successful implementation of all the activities and with a view to motivation we initially lock the payment of tokens to the Yodse project team in the following order: 50% of the tokens due to the team are paid after the ICO, and the second half is frozen and paid only after the 1 January 2020. Similarly, for the long-term motivation of consultants, tokens are paid in the following order:1/3 just after the successfully conducted ICO, 1/3 will be unlocked up to the 1 September 2018 and 1/3 up to the 1 January 2019.  We hope active participants of refferal program will undertand and accept that terms.  Our team is highly motivated to build successful, fast-growing Ecosystem.  Best regards, Alex Rvach

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: Online trading market Working in the online trading market requires new solutions from the participants. After all, this is an undeveloped space with new problems. For example, manufacturers note that the usual marketing techniques do not work in this market and the promotion of goods with the help of IT technologies is too expensive, as is the use of third-party platforms for trade. Buyers in the online market also expects a lot of difficulties, ranging from security issues to difficulties in assessing the goods. Unfortunately, in this market there are still many scammers selling low-quality goods and the abundance of information noise makes it difficult to choose. However, the new blockchain platform Yodse will solve most of them: * Communication. The parties will be able to communicate directly. * Cost. Purchase of goods from the manufacturer is always cheaper than from intermediary. According to some estimates, it is about saving up to 45%. In fact, Yodse ecosystem forms a new level of service, where goods are sold at the lowest prices, but with full information support. By the way, the use of blockchain technologies will allow platform participants to use cryptocurrency for payments among themselves.

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: YODSE — your open direct sales ecosystem is a platform that connects a consumers and manufactures The purpose of the platform is to unite the interests of manufactures and consumers, deleting the boundaries and distances between the countries. Yodse is done to make the real business easier, more profitable, increasing the efficiency and transparency of business by usage of blockchain technology.  The main aim of Yodse is to connect the manufactures and consumers directly without the intermediaries.  Yodse is a global ecosystem that connects directly producers and consumers. The ecosystem is done to to provide the widest choice of high quality products for consumers with a direct guarantee from the manufacturer. Its aim is to reduce the costs associated with the search of the products at a low price.  Yodse offers a transparent and secure transactions thanks to smart contracts. It saves the time, money, minimizing the risks and losses due to the absence of intermediaries. Customer loyalty is guaranteed thanks to the customer-oriented manufacturers. Yodse offers to consumers a direct communication and technical support from the product manufacturers and a fast delivery without the intermediaries.  Among Yodse partners are the large industrial enterprises and transport companies with the extensive experience of the delivery goods all over the world. Thanks partners is guaranteed a timely control and management of deliveries.  Yodse offers to manufactures the growing base of customers and effective business. It helps to increase the sales volumes and net profit of company. Yodse breaks the barrier for small and medium-sized businesses and helps to the development of global trade. The manufactures will have big set of marketing tools for the promotion on the global market. They can place the catalog of their goods without commissions.  The owners of the tokens of Yodse can pay for the services of the platform by tokens. They can participate in the referral program and earn rewards, pay for services and goods of manufacturers and service providers by tokens, use tokens to loan and receive an interest income for loans, improve the work of ecosystem and expand its functionality, to resell the tokens at a favorable rate, to develop the project and its economic efficiency and social partnership.  In order to raise funds for the development of Yodse platform, it was decided to launch an ICO.  Due to the prohibition of advertising of cryptocurrencies, blockchain and ICO on the main social networks Facebook, Twitter, Medium, the blocking of Telegram in Russia, the advertising and promotion of blockchain startups becomes very difficult. The administration of Yodse decided to increase the duration of the Pre-ICO until the 20th of May. During Pre-ICO a 30% discount is available. ICO will be held from the 20th of May to the 30th of July. The maximum discount for ICO is 20%.

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: Yodse ecosystem On its way from the manufacturer to the end customer, a product’s value increases. Sometimes by several times. For final price add the percentage of intermediaries, logistics companies, government, etc. In retail the markup is never noticed, but the additional 1% margin of industrial products could mean thousands of dollars. This approach does not suit either producers or buyers. With the advent of decentralized bases the exit was found.  The ecosystem Yodse (your open direct sales ecosystem), created on the basis of blockchain technologies will become a bridge between the end user of industrial goods and their producers. The use of decentralized databases will ensure to both parties:  transparency of concluded transactions; * secure storage of information and products and transaction information. In other words, Yodse ecosystem already combines the cryptocurrency market and the real economy, introducing the principles of the blockchain networks — security, openness, interaction without intermediaries.

Author: Yodse@Alex
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: regarding the refferal program  Token buyers in the period of pre-ICO and ICO for any amount become participants of referral program and are paid a reward of 5% of the amount of purchases of referrals involved. The first buyers of tokens in the period of pre-ICO and ICO to the amount of at least 1 000 USD are provided with an increased referral rate by 7% compared to the usual token holders. The referral fund of tokens in the amount of 10% of the total issued amount is locked until the 1 January 2019 (except referral payments within the period of pre-ICO and ICO),and further payments to the referrals will be available from the 1 January 2019 in accordance with the referral program.  The purchase of tokens at the early stages will allow purchasers and active holders to influence on the increase of token value, through the referral program. The referral program will be expanded and aimed exclusively at increasing the number of product manufacturers and customers on the marketplace and transactions in the Yodse ecosystem that will contribute to its expansion. These restrictions will not allow to collapse the token value on the stock exchange shortly after the ICO and will set limits to the appearance of a significant number of tokens publicly available on the exchange, as was the case with a large number of ICOs conducted. Thus, we take care that our token buyers funds won’t be affected by the actions of speculators manipulating sales in exchange trade. Moreover, lock of tokens due tothe Yodse team proves its interests and prospects for long-term work and successful implementation of the Yodse project.   Project team is interested in the successful implementation of all the activities and with a view to motivation we initially lock the payment of tokens to the Yodse project team in the following order: 50% of the tokens due to the team are paid after the ICO, and the second half is frozen and paid only after the 1 January 2020. Similarly, for the long-term motivation of consultants, tokens are paid in the following order:1/3 just after the successfully conducted ICO, 1/3 will be unlocked up to the 1 September 2018 and 1/3 up to the 1 January 2019.  We hope active participants of refferal program will undertand and accept that terms.  Our team is highly motivated to build successful, fast-growing Ecosystem.  Best regards, Alex Rvach

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: When creating Yodse platform, we use blockchain technology, and it's not just a beautiful word! Blockchain in our project will make the relationship between buyer and seller as transparent as possible, will allow manufacturers and customers to communicate directly without intermediaries. Using Yodse tokens manufacturers will be able to save on the promotion of their business through the latest marketing technologies, encourage customer loyalty, enjoy all the privileges of the site, get new opportunities in the field of marketing and offer further ways to develop and improve the functioning of the platform. The functionality of our ecosystem will give new opportunities to small and medium-sized businesses to promote products and buyers will be given a wide range of products for which it is possible to pay in Fiat currency as well as in other cryptocurrencies.   We often talk about blockchain technology – it is not a secret to our subscribers that this technology will be used by us when creating Yodse platform. Today we have considered it necessary to tell you a little more about blockchain and how it can be used in our work. So, blockchain is an electronic registry technology that is used to record and store transaction data. The information is stored on the blockchain decentralized, distributed across the network nodes. It is virtually impossible to falsify the data stored in this way, which makes this method of fixing information transparent and as safe as possible. Initially, the blockchain was created to work with cryptocurrencies. Today, companies are exploring various possibilities of blockchain integration into all spheres, including industry and production. For example, IBM Blockchain improves the supply chain and manages data, Blockchain Foundry specializes in services for the production of industrial products, BigChain DB advertises scalable services, and Chain offers a platform for financial services. We are convinced that the integration of blockchain technology in the creation of our service will optimize all internal processes, make the communication of the buyer and the manufacturer more simple and transparent, save time and financial resources.

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: Do you know that according to statistics online trading (including industrial goods) is becoming more popular every day! According to statistics in 2016 about 60.3% of buyers are looking for the necessary goods on the Internet, but only 44.1% of manufacturers use the Internet to provide information about their products, works and services. More than 41% of buyers are willing to buy the goods and services they need via the Internet, but only 19.3% of manufacturers use the Internet to sell their products, and the total production of manufactured goods is about 37 trillion US dollars. It is this market that Yodse service plans to enter! In the realities of the sovereign market, when the Internet has helped buyers become more aware, mobile and informed about products and services, Yodse will allow them to solve problems related to the purchase and sale of goods as efficiently as possible. Our service will take into account the client's need for personalization, will provide them with a wide range of products and services, will help to objectively decide on the purchase through a unique feedback system and a transparent rating system. In turn, we will provide manufacturers with access to international markets, which will contribute to the fact that buyers will be given the right to choose products of higher quality at a lower price! Interested? Find out more on our website and take part in the implementation of a promising project!

Author: posiandu
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐ YODSE ⭐Connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial
Body: YODSE Global ecosystem, directly connecting manufacturers and customers of industrial products.       ICO         [20 May, 2018 - 30 Jul, 2018]         Soft cap: $7,000,000 USD Hard cap: $40,000,000 USD    Abstract  Analysis of multi-billion market of industrial products group and rapidly growing e-commerce market has revealed the gap between end-customer and manufacturer. Yodse (your open direct sales ecosystem) serves as a bridge that will enable the direct communication between customers and manufacturers of industrial products group, promoting loyalty and client - oriented approach. Target group – manufacturers and end-customers of industrial products. Manufacturers of industrial products group – small and medium enterprises, producing small-scale single-pieced articles and also large enterprises, such as:  End-consumers of industrial products group – organizations and individuals, interested in purchasing products directly from manufacturers, and aiming at reducing level of risks, get high-quality technical support from industrial products manufacturers, and also convenient and smooth-running service of product shipping and guaranteed delivery. Yodse will become the largest online ecosystem for the most comfortable, rapid and profitable cooperation between industrial products manufacturers and customers in CIS, Asian and African countries, Europe and USA. Introduction of decentralized and transparent ecosystem Yodse based on blockchain technology ensures success to all participants on the B2B trade marketplace. Ecosystem Yodse (your open direct sales ecosystem) will create: full transaction transparency between manufacturers and customers; decentralized data storage of transactions and products; real economy integration into blockchain and crypto-market;      Benefits  Yodse ecosystem will give manufacturers access to the fundamentally new level of development, which will significantly expand the client base. Yodse offers users advanced, well-predicted, interconnected technological solutions. Ecosystem Yodse will possess a unique resource that will allow manufacturers of industrial products and customers to communicate directly without intermediaries. Using Yodse tokens, manufacturers will be able to save money on the promotion of their business, implement most recent marketing technologies, encourage customer loyalty, enjoy all the privileges of the site, gain new opportunities in the sale of products and offer further ways of development and improving the functioning of the platform. Ecosystem functionality will give new opportunities to the representatives of small and medium-sized businesses for the promotion of their products and provide buyers with a wide range of products for which it is possible to pay both in fiat currency and crypto-currencies. A professional team, decentralized, transparent, and global ecosystem based on the blockchain technology, high-tech products, and convenient user-friendly tools within the ecosystem, as well as the scale of Yodse activities, will enable to achieve top results, satisfying manufacturers, customers and token holders.  The decentralized and transparent Yodse ecosystem will provide: purchase of quality products at prices and direct guarantees from manufacturers; the possibility of saving up to 45% by reducing labor costs, associated with the search for goods, and the opportunity of direct purchase from the manufacturers of industrial goods; reduction of customer risks and losses, bypassing intermediaries; rapid and dynamic growth in the value of the business of manufacturers and customers, which will enhance the investment attractiveness of these companies for shareholders and investors; establishment of the direct communication between customers and the manufacturers; obtaining technical support directly from the manufacturers; increase of customer loyalty and customer mindset of manufacturers; increase of transactions transparency level, control, and management while fulfilling supply and payment activities between consumers and manufacturers; breaking down barriers for small businesses to enter e-commerce and international markets; business growth for manufacturers: customer base, profit and reduce of costs associated with the promotion of goods in the Internet by 3-15% (depending on the allocated costs for these events); purchase of industrial products from manufacturers minimizes the risk of buying regenerated and defected product; the possibility for design and engineering organizations and students to obtain reliable technical and technological information directly from the manufacturers of industrial goods; reduction of manufacturers costs for the outdated marketing technologies;   Roadmap    Our whitepaper: Download Our Official  channels and groups: Facebook  |  Twitter  |  YouTube  |  BOUNTY  |  Telegram HTTP://WWW.YODSE.IO
